properties.title: Beans
properties.description: Louis Abate posted a photo: This was taken using a stack of three extension tubes (68mm in total) on a 100mm lens. I have the Kenko DG's and they work extremely well . Build quality is excellent and they are relatively inexpensive compared to the OEM's. You can do some really neat stuff i.e. fill 2/3rds of a frame with a single jelly bean. Haha.

properties.title: jelly belly
properties.description: beatjoan9 posted a photo: i was stoked to see they now offer this individual-sized serving of my favorite jelly bean derivative. No more having to buy huge containers of the stuff. It is still sitting on my desk at work, because I tried to have resolve and resisted it. But I blew it by eating a bunch of Trolli eggs. Oh well.

properties.title: May 06 2011 [Day 186] "Because You're So Sweet"
properties.description: James_Seattle posted a photo: Because You're So Sweet Jelly Belly Cocktail Classics. I might try one, two, three or all the different flavors though I shouldn't. Rich picked these up last week and I have been staring at the unopened bag since then. They come in six different cocktail flavors: Pomegranate Cosmo, Mojito, Strawberry Daiquiri, Pina Colada, Peach Bellini and Margarita. Erasure, Because You're So Sweet (Partial Lyrics) written by Clarke/Bell from the 1994 release "I Say I Say I Say!". Because you're so sweet You lift up my heart And I'll fall back again But I don't know Quite which way to turn The light in your eyes Touches the sky And I'm your man again And you hold me As close as close can be And many's the time That you've enchanted me Now I want you back Here in my loving arms For eternity You look and you smile Warm me inside Cause you're so good to me A beauty Filled with the joys of spring
